        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Cyber Essentials Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Cybersecurity and Infrastructure Security Agency to develop, publish, and maintain evidence-based guidelines and processes that individuals can follow to defend against common cybersecurity threats and risks. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
